The '/std/dev' inheritable

inherits: ZORKER

Summary: /std/dev is the object used for interactive developers.

New Functions:
set_pwd(string) - set the current working directory
query_pwd() - return the current working directory
set_cwf(string) - set the current working file
query_cwf() - return the current working file
set_start_location(string) - sets the starting location when the
    developer enters the game
query_start_location() - returns the start location

Overloaded Functions:
enter_game(int) - adds support for .login files
init_cmd_hook() - calls set_is_wizard()
die() - overloaded to prevent death
